    ListGenerator, SetGenerator

    public abstract class CollectionGenerator<T extends Collection>
extends ComponentizedGenerator<T>

    Base class for generators of Collections.

    The generated collection has a number of elements limited by GenerationStatus.size(), or else by the attributes of a Size marking. The individual elements will have a type corresponding to the collection's type argument.

      • configure

        public void configure(Size size)

        Tells this generator to add elements to the generated collection a number of times within a specified minimum and/or maximum, inclusive, chosen with uniform distribution.

        Note that some kinds of collections disallow duplicates, so the number of elements added may not be equal to the collection's Collection.size().

        Parameters:
        size - annotation that gives the size constraints
